FBIS4-22000 "jptot016__l94057" JPRS-TOT-94-016-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 13 April 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA ISRAEL Bomb Blast in Hadera Bomb Blast in Hadera Terrorist `Apparently' Among Casualties TA1304154094 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in English 1500 GMT 13 Apr 94 TA1304154094 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el English BFN [Excerpt] Six people were killed this morning and 30 others wounded in a bomb explosion aboard a bus in Hadera. Among the six killed was apparently the terrorist himself. Hamas [Islamic Resistance Movement] has claimed responsibility and says more attacks can be expected. Most of those hurt sustained light injuries, and most of those have already been released from hospital. In Hadera demonstrators protested against the violence and government policy. [passage omitted]
